sequenceDiagram
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator
    participant Istio as Istio Sidecar<br/>mTLS
    participant BuiltIn as Built-In Detector<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant HF as HuggingFace Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Judge as LLM Judge Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant S3 as S3 / MinIO<br/>9000/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM as vLLM Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over S3,HF: Flow 2: Model Initialization (startup)
    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        S3->>HF: KServe Storage Initializer downloads<br/>model weights (AWS credentials)
        HF->>HF: Load model via AutoConfig<br/>(SeqClass / TokClass / CausalLM)
    end

    Note over Orchestrator,BuiltIn: Flow 1: Built-In Text Detection
    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Orchestrator->>Istio: POST /api/v1/text/contents
        Istio->>BuiltIn: Forward (mTLS)<br/>Bearer Token (KServe auth)
        BuiltIn->>BuiltIn: Inline processing<br/>(regex PII, file type, custom)
        BuiltIn-->>Istio: ContentAnalysisResponse
        Istio-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
    end

    Note over Orchestrator,HF: Flow 2: HuggingFace Model-Based Detection
    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Orchestrator->>Istio: POST /api/v1/text/contents
        Istio->>HF: Forward (mTLS)<br/>Bearer Token (KServe auth)
        HF->>HF: GPU/CPU inference<br/>via PyTorch
        HF-->>Istio: ContentAnalysisResponse
        Istio-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
    end

    Note over Orchestrator,vLLM: Flow 3: LLM Judge Detection
    rect rgb(243, 229, 245)
        Orchestrator->>Istio: POST /api/v1/text/contents
        Istio->>Judge: Forward (mTLS)<br/>Bearer Token (KServe auth)
        Judge->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP (cluster-internal, no auth)
        vLLM-->>Judge: LLM evaluation response
        Judge-->>Istio: ContentAnalysisResponse
        Istio-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
    end
